Intelligence?&lt;/h2&gt;&#xD;&#xA;&lt;p&gt;&#xD;&#xA;Artificial Intelligence (AI) is a modern technology that enables machines and software to &#xD;&#xA;think, learn, understand, and make decisions similar to humans. &#xD;&#xA;AI systems can analyze data, recognize patterns, solve problems, and automate tasks.&#xD;&#xA;&lt;/p&gt;</description>
